# REST vs SOAP vs GraphQL

API Type | Data Format Used | Flexibility | Level Implementation Difficulty | Current Usage (High / Medium / Low)

REST     | JSON / XML       | Medium-High | Low                             | High
SOAP     | XML              | Low         | High                            | Low
GraphQL  | JSON             | Very High   | Medium-High                     | Medium

Then answer:
Which do you consider most appropriate for a modern startup developing an online booking system? Why?

GraphQL is most appropriate for a modern startup online booking system because it provides flexible data queries, reduces over-fetching, and enables efficient front-end performance while allowing the API to evolve without breaking clients.
